<i>noun</i>: 확인서 [화긴서], 확인 [화긴] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>확인서 [화긴서]</dt><br>
<dd>confirmation; certificate</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실을 틀림없다고 인정하는 내용의 글이나 서류.</dd><br>
<dd>A statement or document confirming that a certain assertion is true.</dd><br>
<dt>확인 [화긴]</dt><br>
<dd>check; affirmation; confirmation; verification</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러한지를 알아보거나 인정함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of finding out if something is true or admitting that it is true.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>